216bool EndWith(const string& str, const string& ending) {
217 if (str.size() < ending.size()) return false;
218 if (str.substr(str.size() - ending.size(), ending.size()) == ending)
219 return true;
220 return false;
221}
222
223bool IsNodeByLayoutOptimizer(const string& node_name) {
224 const string suffix = kSuffix;
225 return EndWith(node_name, suffix);
226}
227
228bool IsNodeType(const string& node_name, const string& type) {
229 const string suffix = strings::StrCat(type, "-", kSuffix);
230 return EndWith(node_name, suffix);
231}

257bool IsConcat(const NodeDef& node) {
258 const auto op = node.op();
259 return op == "Concat" || op == "ConcatV2";
260}
261
262bool IsConcatV1(const NodeDef& node) {
263 const auto op = node.op();
264 return op == "Concat";
265}
266
267bool IsMaxPoolV2(const NodeDef& node) {
268 const auto& op = node.op();
269 return op == "MaxPoolV2";
270}
271
272bool IsMaxPoolGradV1(const NodeDef& node) {
273 const auto& op = node.op();
274 return op == "MaxPoolGrad";
275}
276
277bool IsMaxPoolGradV2(const NodeDef& node) {
278 const auto& op = node.op();
279 return op == "MaxPoolGradV2";
280}
281
282bool IsMaxPoolGradGradV1(const NodeDef& node) {
283 const auto& op = node.op();
284 return op == "MaxPoolGradGrad";
285}

287bool IsMaxPoolGradGradV2(const NodeDef& node) {
288 const auto& op = node.op();
289 return op == "MaxPoolGradGradV2";

292bool IsUnaryGrad(const NodeDef& node) {
293 bool is_unary_grad =
294 IsEluGrad(node) || IsInvGrad(node) || IsReciprocalGrad(node) ||
295 IsRelu6Grad(node) || IsReluGrad(node) || IsRsqrtGrad(node) ||
296 IsSeluGrad(node) || IsSigmoidGrad(node) || IsSoftplusGrad(node) ||
297 IsSoftsignGrad(node) || IsSqrtGrad(node) || IsTanhGrad(node);
298 return is_unary_grad;
299}
300
301bool IsComparisonOp(const NodeDef& node) {
302 bool is_compare = IsApproximateEqual(node) || IsEqual(node) ||
303 IsGreater(node) || IsGreaterEqual(node) || IsLess(node) ||
304 IsLessEqual(node) || IsNotEqual(node);
305 return is_compare;
306}
307
308bool IsReduceOp(const NodeDef& node) {
309 return IsSum(node) || IsMean(node) || IsProd(node) || IsMax(node) ||
310 IsMin(node) || IsAll(node) || IsAny(node);
311}
312
313bool IsBinaryOp(const NodeDef& node) {
314 bool is_binary =
315 IsAdd(node) || IsAtan2(node) || IsComparisonOp(node) || IsComplex(node) ||
316 IsDiv(node) || IsFloorDiv(node) || IsIgamma(node) || IsIgammac(node) ||
317 IsLogicalAnd(node) || IsLogicalOr(node) || IsMaximum(node) ||
318 IsMinimum(node) || IsMod(node) || IsMul(node) || IsPolygamma(node) ||
319 IsPow(node) || IsRealDiv(node) || IsSquaredDifference(node) ||
320 IsSub(node) || IsTruncateDiv(node) || IsTruncateMod(node) || IsZeta(node);
321 return is_binary;
322}

324std::vector<int> NonControlInputs(const NodeDef& node) {
325 std::vector<int> pos;
326 for (int i = 0; i < node.input_size(); i++) {
327 if (!IsControlInput(node.input(i))) {
328 pos.push_back(i);
329 }
330 }
331 return pos;
332}
333
334std::vector<int> DataInputPosConcat(const NodeDef& node) {
335 int n = node.attr().at("N").i();
336 std::vector<int> input_pos;
337 int start = (IsConcatV1(node)) ? 1 : 0;
338 int end = start + n;
339 for (int i = start; i < end; i++) {
340 input_pos.push_back(i);
341 }
342 return input_pos;
343}
344
345std::vector<int> DataInputPos(const NodeDef& node) {
346 if (IsSplit(node) || IsHistogramSummary(node)) {
347 return {1};
348 }
349 if (IsStridedSliceGrad(node)) {
350 return {4};
351 }
352 if (IsBinaryOp(node) || IsUnaryGrad(node)) {
353 return {0, 1};
354 }
355 if (IsBetainc(node) || IsSelect(node)) {
356 return {0, 1, 2};
357 }
358 if (IsShapeN(node) || IsIdentityN(node) || IsAddN(node) || IsMerge(node)) {
359 return NonControlInputs(node);
360 }
361 if (IsConcat(node)) {
362 return DataInputPosConcat(node);
363 }
364 if (node.input_size() > 0 && !IsControlInput(node.input(0))) {
365 return {0};
366 }
367 return {};
368}
369
370bool IsHostMemory(const NodeDef& node, int output_port) {
371 DeviceNameUtils::ParsedName parsed_name;
372 if (DeviceNameUtils::ParseFullName(node.device(), &parsed_name)) {
373 DeviceType device_type(parsed_name.type);
374 Status s = FindKernelDef(device_type, node, nullptr, nullptr);
375 if (s.ok()) {
376 tensorflow::MemoryTypeVector in_mtypes;
377 tensorflow::MemoryTypeVector out_mtypes;
378 s = tensorflow::MemoryTypesForNode(OpRegistry::Global(), device_type,
379 node, &in_mtypes, &out_mtypes);
380 if (s.ok()) {
381 if (out_mtypes[output_port] == HOST_MEMORY) {
382 return true;
383 }
384 }
385 } else {
386 return true;
387 }
388 }
389 return false;
390}

392class GraphProcessor {
393 public:
394 GraphProcessor(const GraphProperties& graph_properties,
395 const VirtualPlacer& virtual_placer,
396 const std::unordered_set<string>& nodes_to_preserve,
397 GraphDef* graph, NodeMap* node_map)
398 : graph_properties_(graph_properties),
399 virtual_placer_(virtual_placer),
400 nodes_to_preserve_(nodes_to_preserve),
401 graph_(graph),
402 node_map_(node_map) {}
403
404 protected:
405 NodeDef* AddNodePermConst(const string& name, const string& device,
406 const std::vector<int>& permutation) {
407 NodeDef* node = graph_->add_node();
408 node_map_->AddNode(name, node);
409 node->set_name(name);
410 node->set_op("Const");
411 AttrValue attr_data_type;
412 attr_data_type.set_type(DT_INT32);
413 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"dtype", attr_data_type});
414 AttrValue attr_tensor;
415 Tensor tensor(DT_INT32, TensorShape({4}));
416 for (int i = 0; static_cast<size_t>(i) < permutation.size(); i++) {
417 tensor.flat<int>()(i) = permutation[i];
418 }
419 tensor.AsProtoTensorContent(attr_tensor.mutable_tensor());
420 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"value", attr_tensor});
421 string device_name;
422 if (device.empty()) {
423 device_name = virtual_placer_.get_canonical_device_name(*node);
424 } else {
425 device_name = device;
426 }
427 node->set_device(device_name);
428 return node;
429 }
430
431 NodeDef* AddNodeConstScalar(const string& name, const string& device,
432 DataType dtype, int value) {
433 NodeDef* node = graph_->add_node();
434 node_map_->AddNode(name, node);
435 node->set_name(name);
436 node->set_op("Const");
437 AttrValue attr_data_type;
438 attr_data_type.set_type(dtype);
439 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"dtype", attr_data_type});
440 AttrValue attr_tensor;
441 Tensor tensor(dtype, TensorShape({}));
442 tensor.scalar<int>()() = value;
443 tensor.AsProtoTensorContent(attr_tensor.mutable_tensor());
444 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"value", attr_tensor});
445 string device_name;
446 if (device.empty()) {
447 device_name = virtual_placer_.get_canonical_device_name(*node);
448 } else {
449 device_name = device;
450 }
451 node->set_device(device_name);
452 return node;
453 }
454
455 string LayoutOptimizerNode(const string& base_name) {
456 return strings::StrCat(base_name, "-", kSuffix);
457 }
458
459 const GraphProperties& graph_properties_;
460 const VirtualPlacer& virtual_placer_;
461 const std::unordered_set<string>& nodes_to_preserve_;
462 GraphDef* graph_;
463 NodeMap* node_map_;
464};
465
466struct OptimizeContext {
467 OptimizeContext(GraphDef* graph, NodeDef* node, NodeMap* node_map,
468 const GraphProperties& graph_properties,
469 const VirtualPlacer& virtual_placer,
470 const std::unordered_set<string>& nodes_to_preserve,
471 bool is_in_frame)
472 : graph(graph),
473 node(node),
474 node_map(node_map),
475 graph_properties(graph_properties),
476 virtual_placer(virtual_placer),
477 nodes_to_preserve(nodes_to_preserve),
478 is_in_frame(is_in_frame) {}
479 GraphDef* graph;
480 NodeDef* node;
481 NodeMap* node_map;
482 const GraphProperties& graph_properties;
483 const VirtualPlacer& virtual_placer;
484 const std::unordered_set<string>& nodes_to_preserve;
485 bool is_in_frame;
486};
487
488class NodeProcessor : public GraphProcessor {
489 public:
490 explicit NodeProcessor(const OptimizeContext& opt_cxt)
491 : GraphProcessor(opt_cxt.graph_properties, opt_cxt.virtual_placer,
492 opt_cxt.nodes_to_preserve, opt_cxt.graph,
493 opt_cxt.node_map),
494 node_(opt_cxt.node),
495 is_in_frame_(opt_cxt.is_in_frame) {}
496 virtual ~NodeProcessor() {}
497 virtual Status ConvertNode() {
498 if (ShouldProcess()) {
499 UpdateAttrDataFormat();
500 UpdateAttrKSize();
501 UpdateAttrStrides();
502 UpdateAttrShape();
503 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(AddLayoutTransposeToInputs());
504 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(AddLayoutTransposeToOutputs());
505 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(CustomizedProcessing());
506 }
507 return Status::OK();
508 }
509
510 protected:
511 bool IsPortDimsN(const NodeDef& node, int port, int n) const {
512 if (node.attr().find("_output_shapes") != node.attr().end()) {
513 if (node.attr().at("_output_shapes").list().shape_size() > port) {
514 auto shape = node.attr().at("_output_shapes").list().shape(port);
515 if (shape.unknown_rank()) {
516 return false;
517 }
518 if (shape.dim_size() == n) {
519 return true;
520 }
521 }
522 }
523 return false;
524 }
525
526 bool IsPortZeroDimsN(const NodeDef& node, int n) const {
527 return IsPortDimsN(node, 0, n);
528 }
529
530 bool IsPortZeroDimsFour(const NodeDef& node) const {
531 return NodeProcessor::IsPortZeroDimsN(node, 4) ||
532 IsTransposeNCHWToNHWC(node.name());
533 }
534
535 bool IsPortDimsFour(const NodeDef& node, int port) const {
536 return NodeProcessor::IsPortDimsN(node, port, 4) ||
537 IsTransposeNCHWToNHWC(node.name());
538 }
539
540 bool IsNHWC() const {
541 if (node_->attr().find("data_format") != node_->attr().end()) {
542 if (node_->attr().at("data_format").s().compare("NHWC") == 0) {
543 return true;
544 }
545 }
546 return false;
547 }
548
549 bool HasOutputs() const {
550 auto outputs = node_map_->GetOutputs(node_->name());
551 return !outputs.empty();
552 }
553
554 Status HasAttribute(const NodeDef& node, const string& attr) const {
555 if (node.attr().find(attr) == node.attr().end()) {
556 return Status(error::INVALID_ARGUMENT,
557 strings::StrCat("Missing attribute ", attr));
558 }
559 return Status::OK();
560 }
561
562 bool MustPreserve() const {
563 return nodes_to_preserve_.find(node_->name()) != nodes_to_preserve_.end();
564 }
565
566 bool IsOnGPU() const {
567 string device_name;
568 if (node_->device().empty()) {
569 device_name = virtual_placer_.get_canonical_device_name(*node_);
570 } else {
571 device_name = node_->device();
572 }
573 string device;
574 string not_used;
575 if (DeviceNameUtils::SplitDeviceName(device_name, &not_used, &device) &&
576 str_util::StrContains(str_util::Lowercase(device),
577 str_util::Lowercase(DEVICE_GPU))) {
578 return true;
579 }
580 return false;
581 }
582
583 virtual bool ShouldProcess() const {
584 return !MustPreserve() && IsNHWC() && IsPortZeroDimsFour(*node_) &&
585 HasOutputs() && IsOnGPU();
586 }
587
588 virtual void UpdateAttrShape() {
589 if (node_->attr().find("_output_shapes") != node_->attr().end()) {
590 for (const auto& pos : GetOutputPos()) {
591 auto shape = node_->mutable_attr()
592 ->at("_output_shapes")
593 .mutable_list()
594 ->mutable_shape(pos);
595 if (shape->dim_size() == 4) {
596 int64 h = shape->dim(1).size();
597 int64 w = shape->dim(2).size();
598 int64 c = shape->dim(3).size();
599 shape->mutable_dim(1)->set_size(c);
600 shape->mutable_dim(2)->set_size(h);
601 shape->mutable_dim(3)->set_size(w);
602 }
603 }
604 }
605 }
606
607 Status UpdateAttrValueOfInput(int input_index, bool permute) {
608 auto input_node = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(input_index));
609 // We created a copy of the node, so that we don't modify the original node,
610 // which might be used elsewhere. Note that this copy also copies the
611 // control dependency input in the case this node is inside a loop,
612 // to ensure added_node is in the same frame with node_.
613 NodeDef* added_node = graph_->add_node();
614 *added_node = *input_node;
615 string base_name = strings::StrCat(node_->name(), "-", input_index);
616 string node_name = LayoutOptimizerNode(base_name);
617 added_node->set_name(node_name);
618 *node_->mutable_input(input_index) = node_name;
619 node_map_->AddNode(node_name, added_node);
620 node_map_->AddOutput(node_name, node_->name());
621 return UpdateAttrValue(added_node, permute);
622 }
623
624 virtual std::vector<int> GetInputPos() const { return {0}; }
625
626 virtual std::set<int> GetOutputPos() const {
627 // For most nodes, no need to process control nodes or nodes that use an
628 // output other than the first output: only the first output is of
629 // 4D NCHW/NHWC format and thus relevant here.
630 std::set<int> output_pos = {0};
631 return output_pos;
632 }
633
634 virtual Status AddLayoutTransposeToInputs() {
635 std::vector<int> input_pos = GetInputPos();
636 for (const auto& pos : input_pos) {
637 string node_name = LayoutOptimizerNode(
638 strings::StrCat(node_->name(), "-", pos, "-", kTransposeNHWCToNCHW));
639 DataType dtype =
640 graph_properties_.GetInputProperties(node_->name())[pos].dtype();
641 auto input_node = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(pos));
642 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(HasAttribute(*input_node, "_output_shapes"));
643 string const_name = GetOrAddNodePermNHWCToNCHW(pos);
644 int output_pos;
645 ParseNodeName(node_->input(pos), &output_pos);
646 AddNodeTranspose(
647 node_name, node_->input(pos), const_name, dtype,
648 input_node->attr().at("_output_shapes").list().shape(output_pos),
649 true);
650 node_map_->UpdateOutput(NodeName(node_->input(pos)), node_->name(),
651 node_name);
652 node_map_->AddOutput(node_name, node_->name());
653 *node_->mutable_input(pos) = node_name;
654 }
655 return Status::OK();
656 }
657
658 Status AddTransformToOutputs(const string& op) {
659 auto outputs = node_map_->GetOutputs(node_->name());
660 string const_name = GetOrAddNodePermNCHWToNHWC();
661 int output_count = 0;
662 for (const auto& output : outputs) {
663 int connections = 0;
664 int connections_removed = 0;
665 for (int i = 0; i < output->input_size(); i++) {
666 auto& input = *output->mutable_input(i);
667 int input_port;
668 string input_name = ParseNodeName(input, &input_port);
669 auto output_pos = GetOutputPos();
670 if (input_name == node_->name()) {
671 connections++;
672 if (output_pos.find(input_port) != output_pos.end()) {
673 connections_removed++;
674 string added_node_base_name =
675 strings::StrCat(node_->name(), "-", output_count, "-", i);
676 string added_node_name;
677 DataType dtype =
678 graph_properties_.GetOutputProperties(node_->name())[input_port]
679 .dtype();
680 if (op == "Transpose") {
681 added_node_name = LayoutOptimizerNode(strings::StrCat(
682 added_node_base_name, "-", kTransposeNCHWToNHWC));
683 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(HasAttribute(*node_, "_output_shapes"));
684 AddNodeTranspose(
685 added_node_name, input, const_name, dtype,
686 node_->attr().at("_output_shapes").list().shape(input_port),
687 false);
688 } else if (op == "DataFormatVecPermute") {
689 added_node_name = LayoutOptimizerNode(strings::StrCat(
690 added_node_base_name, "-", kVecPermuteNCHWToNHWC));
691 AddNodeDataFormatOp(added_node_name, input, op, dtype, false);
692 } else {
693 return errors::InvalidArgument("Unsupported op type: ", op);
694 }
695 input = added_node_name;
696 node_map_->AddOutput(node_->name(), added_node_name);
697 node_map_->AddOutput(added_node_name, output->name());
698 }
699 }
700 }
701 if (connections == connections_removed) {
702 node_map_->RemoveOutput(node_->name(), output->name());
703 }
704 output_count++;
705 }
706 return Status::OK();
707 }
708
709 virtual Status AddLayoutTransposeToOutputs() {
710 return AddTransformToOutputs("Transpose");
711 }

716 DataType dtype) {
717 auto param_node = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(param_index));
718 bool permute = (op == "DataFormatVecPermute") ? true : false;
719 if (IsConstant(*param_node)) {

721 } else {
722 AddDataFormatTranformToParamInput(op, param_index, dtype);
723 }
724 return Status::OK();

745 void UpdateAttrDataFormat() {
746 if (node_->attr().find("data_format") != node_->attr().end()) {
747 if (node_->attr().at("data_format").s().compare("NHWC") == 0) {
748 string* data_format =
749 node_->mutable_attr()->at("data_format").mutable_s();

754
755 Status UpdateAttrValue(NodeDef* node, bool permute) {
756 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(HasAttribute(*node, "value"));
757 Tensor tensor;
758 auto success =
759 tensor.FromProto(node->mutable_attr()->at({"value"}).tensor());
760 if (!success) {
761 LOG(ERROR) << "Failed to parse TensorProto.";
762 }
763
764 if (permute) {
765 if (tensor.dims() == 1) {
766 if (tensor.flat<int>().size() == 4) {
767 int c = tensor.flat<int>()(3);
768 tensor.flat<int>()(3) = tensor.flat<int>()(2);
769 tensor.flat<int>()(2) = tensor.flat<int>()(1);
770 tensor.flat<int>()(1) = c;
771 } else {
772 return Status(error::INVALID_ARGUMENT,
773 strings::StrCat("Unsupported tensor size: ",
774 tensor.flat<int>().size()));
775 }
776 } else if (tensor.dims() == 2) {
777 for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
778 int c = tensor.matrix<int>()(3, i);
779 tensor.matrix<int>()(3, i) = tensor.matrix<int>()(2, i);
780 tensor.matrix<int>()(2, i) = tensor.matrix<int>()(1, i);
781 tensor.matrix<int>()(1, i) = c;
782 }
783 } else {
784 return Status(
785 error::INVALID_ARGUMENT,
786 strings::StrCat("Unsupported dimension size: ", tensor.dims()));
787 }
788 } else {
789 for (int i = 0; i < tensor.flat<int>().size(); i++) {
790 int value = tensor.flat<int>()(i);
791 value = (value >= 0) ? value : value + 4;
792 if (value == 1 || value == 2) {
793 value = value + 1;
794 } else if (value == 3) {
795 value = 1;
796 }
797 tensor.flat<int>()(i) = value;
798 }
799 }
800
801 if (tensor.dims() == 0) {
802 tensor.AsProtoField(node->mutable_attr()->at({"value"}).mutable_tensor());
803 } else {
804 tensor.AsProtoTensorContent(
805 node->mutable_attr()->at({"value"}).mutable_tensor());
806 }
807 return Status::OK();
808 }

810 NodeDef* AddNodeTranspose(const string& node_name, const string& input_name,
811 const string& const_name, DataType data_type,
812 const TensorShapeProto& input_shape,
813 bool NHWCToNCHW) {
814 NodeDef* node = graph_->add_node();
815 node_map_->AddNode(node_name, node);
816 node->set_name(node_name);
817 *node->add_input() = input_name;
818 *node->add_input() = const_name;
819 node->set_op("Transpose");
820 node->set_device(node_->device());
821 AttrValue attr_data_type;
822 attr_data_type.set_type(data_type);
823 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"T", attr_data_type});
824 AttrValue attr_data_type_perm;
825 attr_data_type_perm.set_type(DT_INT32);
826 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"Tperm", attr_data_type_perm});
827 if (!input_shape.unknown_rank()) {
828 AttrValue attr_output_shape;
829 auto output_shape = attr_output_shape.mutable_list()->add_shape();
830 if (NHWCToNCHW) {
831 output_shape->add_dim()->set_size(input_shape.dim(0).size());
832 output_shape->add_dim()->set_size(input_shape.dim(3).size());
833 output_shape->add_dim()->set_size(input_shape.dim(1).size());
834 output_shape->add_dim()->set_size(input_shape.dim(2).size());
835 } else {
836 output_shape->add_dim()->set_size(input_shape.dim(0).size());
837 output_shape->add_dim()->set_size(input_shape.dim(2).size());
838 output_shape->add_dim()->set_size(input_shape.dim(3).size());
839 output_shape->add_dim()->set_size(input_shape.dim(1).size());
840 }
841 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"_output_shapes", attr_output_shape});
842 }
843 return node;
844 }

912 string MaybeGetHostDevice(const string& input_name) const {
913 string device = node_->device();
914 DeviceNameUtils::ParsedName parsed_name;
915 if (DeviceNameUtils::ParseFullName(device, &parsed_name)) {
916 if (parsed_name.type != "CPU") {
917 NodeDef* input = node_map_->GetNode(input_name);
918 int port;
919 ParseNodeName(input_name, &port);
920 if (IsHostMemory(*input, port)) {
921 parsed_name.type = "CPU";
922 parsed_name.id = 0;
923 device = DeviceNameUtils::ParsedNameToString(parsed_name);
924 }
925 }
926 }
927 return device;

930 NodeDef* AddNodeDataFormatOp(const string& name, const string& input_name,
931 const string& op, DataType dtype,
932 bool nhwc_to_nchw) {
933 NodeDef* added_node = graph_->add_node();
934 added_node->set_name(name);
935 added_node->set_op(op);
936 node_map_->AddNode(added_node->name(), added_node);
937 // The inputs of a DataFormat op could be in host memory for ops such as
938 // Reshape.
939 added_node->set_device(MaybeGetHostDevice(input_name));
940 AttrValue attr_data_type;
941 attr_data_type.set_type(dtype);
942 added_node->mutable_attr()->insert({"T", attr_data_type});
943 string src_format = (nhwc_to_nchw) ? "NHWC" : "NCHW";
944 string dst_format = (nhwc_to_nchw) ? "NCHW" : "NHWC";
945 AttrValue attr_format;
946 attr_format.set_s(src_format);
947 added_node->mutable_attr()->insert({"src_format", attr_format});
948 attr_format.set_s(dst_format);
949 added_node->mutable_attr()->insert({"dst_format", attr_format});
950 *added_node->add_input() = input_name;
951 return added_node;
952 }

1019 TensorShapeProto GetShape(const string& input_name) const {
1020 string node_name;
1021 int output_pos;
1022 node_name = ParseNodeName(input_name, &output_pos);
1023 NodeDef* node = node_map_->GetNode(node_name);
1024 if (node->attr().find("_output_shapes") != node->attr().end()) {
1025 return node->attr().at("_output_shapes").list().shape(output_pos);
1026 }
1027 TensorShapeProto shape;
1028 return shape;
1029 }
1030
1031 bool IsStrideOne() const {
1032 if (node_->attr().find("strides") != node_->attr().end()) {
1033 auto list = node_->attr().at("strides").list();
1034 return list.i(1) == 1 && list.i(2) == 1;
1035 }

1037 }
1038
1039 bool IsValidPadding() const {
1040 if (node_->attr().find("padding") != node_->attr().end()) {
1041 auto padding = node_->attr().at("padding").s();
1042 return padding == "VALID";
1043 }
1044 return false;
1045 }
1046
1047 // The logic inside this function is based on the internal implementation of
1048 // Conv2D, Conv2DBackpropInput, and Conv2DBackpropFilter ops, and thus
1049 // needs to be updated accordingly if the internal implementation changes.
1050 bool IsGemmUsed(const TensorShapeProto& filter_shape,
1051 const TensorShapeProto& input_shape) const {
1052 if (filter_shape.dim_size() == 4) {
1053 if (filter_shape.dim(0).size() == 1 && filter_shape.dim(1).size() == 1 &&
1054 IsStrideOne()) {
1055 return true;
1056 }
1057 }
1058 if (input_shape.dim_size() == 4 && filter_shape.dim_size() == 4) {
1059 if (input_shape.dim(1).size() == filter_shape.dim(0).size() &&
1060 input_shape.dim(2).size() == filter_shape.dim(1).size() &&
1061 IsValidPadding()) {
1062 return true;
1063 }
1064 }
1065 return false;
1066 }
1067
1068 virtual bool IsGemmUsed() const {
1069 auto filter_shape = GetShape(node_->input(1));
1070 auto input_shape = GetShape(node_->input(0));
1071 return IsGemmUsed(filter_shape, input_shape);
1072 }
1073
1074 bool no_gemm_;

1190class AgnosticNodeProcessor : public NodeProcessor {
1191 public:
1192 explicit AgnosticNodeProcessor(const OptimizeContext& opt_cxt)
1193 : NodeProcessor(opt_cxt) {}
1194
1195 protected:
1196 bool ShouldProcess() const override {
1197 return !MustPreserve() && IsPortZeroDimsFour(*node_) && HasOutputs() &&
1198 IsNodeAfterNCHWToNHWC() && IsOnGPU();
1199 }
1200
1201 bool IsNodeAfterNCHWToNHWC(const NodeDef& node) const {
1202 std::set<string> ops_format_agnostic = GetOpsFormatAgnostic();
1203 std::deque<NodeDef*> queue;
1204 auto data_node_pos = DataInputPos(node);
1205 std::unordered_set<string> visited;
1206 for (const auto& pos : data_node_pos) {
1207 auto input_node = node_map_->GetNode(node.input(pos));
1208 queue.push_back(input_node);
1209 visited.insert(input_node->name());
1210 }
1211 // The code will exit this while loop in one iteration in most cases, as the
1212 // graph is already topologically sorted.
1213 while (!queue.empty()) {
1214 NodeDef* current_node = queue.front();
1215 queue.pop_front();
1216 if (IsTransposeNCHWToNHWC(current_node->name()) ||
1217 IsDimMapNCHWToNHWC(current_node->name()) ||
1218 IsVecPermuteNCHWToNHWC(current_node->name())) {
1219 return true;
1220 }
1221 // We only continue searching if the path is connected through
1222 // format-agnostic nodes.
1223 if (ops_format_agnostic.find(current_node->op()) !=
1224 ops_format_agnostic.end()) {
1225 auto current_node_pos = DataInputPos(*current_node);
1226 for (const auto& pos : current_node_pos) {
1227 auto input_node = node_map_->GetNode(current_node->input(pos));
1228 if (visited.find(input_node->name()) == visited.end()) {
1229 queue.push_back(input_node);
1230 visited.insert(input_node->name());
1231 }
1232 }
1233 }
1234 }
1235 return false;
1236 }
1237
1238 bool IsNodeAfterNCHWToNHWC() const { return IsNodeAfterNCHWToNHWC(*node_); }
1239};

1252class BinaryOpProcessor : public AgnosticNodeProcessor {
1253 public:
1254 explicit BinaryOpProcessor(const OptimizeContext& opt_cxt)
1255 : AgnosticNodeProcessor(opt_cxt) {}
1256
1257 protected:
1258 bool ShouldProcess() const override {
1259 return !MustPreserve() && IsPortZeroDimsFour(*node_) && HasOutputs() &&
1260 IsNodeAfterNCHWToNHWC() &&
1261 (IsNDOperateWithMD(4, 0) || IsNDOperateWithMD(4, 1) ||
1262 IsNDOperateWithMD(4, 4) || IsNDOperateWithMD(0, 4) ||
1263 IsNDOperateWithMD(1, 4)) &&
1264 IsOnGPU();
1265 }
1266
1267 std::vector<int> GetInputPos() const override {
1268 std::vector<int> input_pos;
1269 auto input0 = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(0));
1270 auto input1 = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(1));
1271 int input0_port;
1272 ParseNodeName(node_->input(0), &input0_port);
1273 int input1_port;
1274 ParseNodeName(node_->input(1), &input1_port);
1275 if (IsPortDimsFour(*input0, input0_port)) {
1276 input_pos.push_back(0);
1277 }
1278 if (IsPortDimsFour(*input1, input1_port)) {
1279 input_pos.push_back(1);
1280 }
1281 return input_pos;
1282 }
1283
1284 bool IsNDOperateWithMD(int n, int m) const {
1285 auto input0 = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(0));
1286 auto input1 = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(1));
1287 int input0_port;
1288 ParseNodeName(node_->input(0), &input0_port);
1289 int input1_port;
1290 ParseNodeName(node_->input(1), &input1_port);
1291
1292 if (input0 && input1) {
1293 bool input0_is_n = (n == 4) ? IsPortDimsFour(*input0, input0_port)
1294 : IsPortDimsN(*input0, input0_port, n);
1295 bool input1_is_m = (m == 4) ? IsPortDimsFour(*input1, input1_port)
1296 : IsPortDimsN(*input1, input1_port, m);
1297 return input0_is_n && input1_is_m;
1298 }
1299 return false;
1300 }

1302 NodeDef* AddNodeShapeConst(const string& name, int num_channels,
1303 const string& depended_node) {
1304 NodeDef* node = graph_->add_node();
1305 node_map_->AddNode(name, node);
1306 node->set_name(name);
1307 node->set_op("Const");
1308 node->set_device(node_->device());
1309 AttrValue attr_data_type;
1310 attr_data_type.set_type(DT_INT32);
1311 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"dtype", attr_data_type});
1312
1313 AttrValue attr_tensor;
1314 Tensor tensor(DT_INT32, TensorShape({4}));
1315 std::vector<int> shape = {1, num_channels, 1, 1};
1316 for (int i = 0; i < static_cast<int>(shape.size()); i++) {
1317 tensor.flat<int>()(i) = shape[i];
1318 }
1319 tensor.AsProtoTensorContent(attr_tensor.mutable_tensor());
1320 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"value", attr_tensor});
1321 if (is_in_frame_) {
1322 // This is to ensure the transpose node and the const node are in the
1323 // same frame.
1324 *node->add_input() = AsControlDependency(depended_node);
1325 }
1326 return node;
1327 }

1329 NodeDef* AddNodeReshape(const string& node_name, const string& input_name,
1330 const string& shape_const_node_name,
1331 DataType data_type) {
1332 NodeDef* node = graph_->add_node();
1333 node_map_->AddNode(node_name, node);
1334 node->set_name(node_name);
1335 *node->add_input() = input_name;
1336 *node->add_input() = shape_const_node_name;
1337 node->set_op("Reshape");
1338 node->set_device(node_->device());
1339
1340 AttrValue attr_type_indices;
1341 attr_type_indices.set_type(DT_INT32);
1342 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"Tshape", attr_type_indices});
1343
1344 AttrValue attr_type_params;
1345 attr_type_params.set_type(data_type);
1346 node->mutable_attr()->insert({"T", attr_type_params});
1347 return node;
1348 }
1349
1350 Status CustomizedProcessing() override {
1351 int vector_index = -1;
1352 if (IsNDOperateWithMD(4, 1)) {
1353 vector_index = 1;
1354 } else if (IsNDOperateWithMD(1, 4)) {
1355 vector_index = 0;
1356 }
1357 if (vector_index != -1) {
1358 string base_name = strings::StrCat(node_->name(), "-", vector_index);
1359 string reshape_node_name = LayoutOptimizerNode(
1360 strings::StrCat(base_name, "-", kReshapeNHWCToNCHW));
1361 string shape_const_node_name =
1362 LayoutOptimizerNode(strings::StrCat(base_name, "-", kReshapeConst));
1363 auto input_node = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(vector_index));
1364 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(HasAttribute(*input_node, "_output_shapes"));
1365 int port;
1366 ParseNodeName(node_->input(vector_index), &port);
1367 int vector_size = input_node->attr()
1368 .at("_output_shapes")
1369 .list()
1370 .shape(port)
1371 .dim(0)
1372 .size();
1373 AddNodeShapeConst(shape_const_node_name, vector_size,
1374 NodeName(node_->input(vector_index)));
1375 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(HasAttribute(*node_, "T"));
1376 AddNodeReshape(reshape_node_name, node_->input(vector_index),
1377 shape_const_node_name, node_->attr().at("T").type());
1378 node_map_->AddOutput(shape_const_node_name, reshape_node_name);
1379 node_map_->UpdateOutput(NodeName(node_->input(vector_index)),
1380 node_->name(), reshape_node_name);
1381 node_map_->AddOutput(reshape_node_name, node_->name());
1382 *node_->mutable_input(vector_index) = reshape_node_name;
1383 }
1384 return Status::OK();
1385 }

1704 }

1707 return IsMaskZero("ellipsis_mask") && IsMaskZero("new_axis_mask") &&
1708 IsMaskZero("shrink_axis_mask");

1710
1711 Status UpdateMask(const string& mask) {
1712 int i = node_->attr().at(mask).i();
1713 if (i < 0 || i > 15) {
1714 return errors::InvalidArgument("invalid mask value: ", i);
1715 }
1716 if (i == 0 || i == 1 || i == 14 || i == 15) return Status::OK();
1717 switch (i) {
1718 case 2:
1719 case 3:
1720 i += 2;
1721 break;
1722 case 4:
1723 case 5:
1724 i += 4;
1725 break;
1726 case 6:
1727 case 7:
1728 i += 6;
1729 break;
1730 case 8:
1731 case 9:
1732 i -= 6;
1733 break;
1734 case 10:
1735 case 11:
1736 i -= 4;
1737 break;
1738 case 12:
1739 case 13:
1740 i -= 2;
1741 break;
1742 }
1743 node_->mutable_attr()->at(mask).set_i(i);
1744 return Status::OK();
1745 }

1760class SqueezeProcessor : public AgnosticNodeProcessor {
1761 public:
1762 explicit SqueezeProcessor(const OptimizeContext& opt_cxt)
1763 : AgnosticNodeProcessor(opt_cxt) {}
1764
1765 protected:
1766 bool ShouldProcess() const override {
1767 bool is_dims_supported = (IsPortZeroDimsN(*node_, 2) && IsAlongHW()) ||
1768 (IsPortZeroDimsN(*node_, 1) && IsAlongNHW());
1769 return !MustPreserve() && HasOutputs() && IsNodeAfterNCHWToNHWC() &&
1770 IsInputConvertible() && is_dims_supported && IsOnGPU();
1771 }
1772
1773 Status AddLayoutTransposeToOutputs() override { return Status::OK(); }
1774
1775 Status CustomizedProcessing() override {
1776 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(HasAttribute(*node_, "squeeze_dims"));
1777 auto list = node_->mutable_attr()->at("squeeze_dims").mutable_list();
1778 if (list->i_size() == 2) {
1779 list->set_i(0, 2);
1780 list->set_i(1, 3);
1781 } else if (list->i_size() == 3) {
1782 list->set_i(1, 2);
1783 list->set_i(2, 3);
1784 }
1785 return Status::OK();
1786 }
1787
1788 private:
1789 bool IsInputConvertible() const {
1790 int input_port;
1791 auto input = node_map_->GetNode(node_->input(0));
1792 ParseNodeName(node_->input(0), &input_port);
1793 if (input->attr().find("_output_shapes") != input->attr().end()) {
1794 auto shape = input->attr().at("_output_shapes").list().shape(input_port);
1795 if (shape.dim_size() != 4) {
1796 return false;
1797 }
1798 if (shape.dim(1).size() == 1 && shape.dim(2).size() == 1) {
1799 return true;
1800 }
1801 if (shape.dim(0).size() == 1 && shape.dim(1).size() == 1 &&
1802 shape.dim(2).size() == 1) {
1803 return true;
1804 }
1805 }
1806 return false;
1807 }
1808
1809 bool IsAlongAxis(const std::vector<int>& axis) const {
1810 if (node_->attr().find("squeeze_dims") != node_->attr().end()) {
1811 auto list = node_->attr().at("squeeze_dims").list();
1812 // If list is empty, Squeeze op will squeeze all dimensions of size 1.
1813 if (list.i_size() == 0) return true;
1814 if (list.i_size() == axis.size()) {
1815 bool along_axis = true;
1816 for (int i = 0; i < axis.size(); i++) {
1817 along_axis = along_axis && (list.i(i) == axis[i]);
1818 }
1819 if (along_axis) return true;
1820 }
1821 }
1822 return false;
1823 }
1824 bool IsAlongHW() const { return IsAlongAxis({1, 2}); }
1825 bool IsAlongNHW() const { return IsAlongAxis({0, 1, 2}); }
1826};

1872 Tensor tensor;
1873 auto success = tensor.FromProto(axis_node->attr().at({"value"}).tensor());
1874 if (!success) {
1875 LOG(ERROR) << "Failed to parse TensorProto.";
1876 }
1877 if (tensor.dims() == 1 && tensor.dim_size(0) == axis.size()) {
1878 bool along_axis = true;
1879 for (int i = 0; i < axis.size(); i++) {
1880 along_axis = along_axis && (tensor.flat<int>()(i) == axis[i]);

1882 if (along_axis) return true;

1921
1922class DataLayoutOptimizer : GraphProcessor {
1923 public:
1924 explicit DataLayoutOptimizer(
1925 const GraphProperties& graph_properties,
1926 const VirtualPlacer& virtual_placer,
1927 const LayoutOptimizer::TuningConfig& config,
1928 const std::unordered_set<string>& nodes_to_preserve, GraphDef* graph,
1929 NodeMap* node_map)
1930 : GraphProcessor(graph_properties, virtual_placer, nodes_to_preserve,
1931 graph, node_map),
1932 config_(config) {}
1933
1934 Status Optimize() {
1935 VLOG(1) << "Number of nodes for original graph: " << graph_->node_size();
1936 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(Expand());
1937 VLOG(1) << "Number of nodes after Expand: " << graph_->node_size();
1938 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(Collapse());
1939 VLOG(1) << "Number of nodes after Collapse: " << graph_->node_size();
1940 return Status::OK();
1941 }
1942
1943 private:
1944 NodeDef* AddNodePermNHWCToNCHW() {
1945 return AddNodePermConst(LayoutOptimizerNode(kPermNHWCToNCHW), "",
1946 {0, 3, 1, 2});
1947 }
1948
1949 NodeDef* AddNodePermNCHWToNHWC() {
1950 return AddNodePermConst(LayoutOptimizerNode(kPermNCHWToNHWC), "",
1951 {0, 2, 3, 1});
1952 }
1953
1954 // Expand all nodes which is in NHWC, but supports NCHW or is layout agnostic.
1955 Status Expand() {
1956 int node_size_original = graph_->node_size();
1957 std::unordered_map<const NodeDef*, std::vector<int>> frames;
1958 int num_frames;
1959 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(IdentifyFrames(*graph_, &frames, &num_frames));
1960
1961 // This is the first pass where we expand the nodes which support NCHW.
1962 std::set<string> ops_format_supported = GetOpsFormatSupported();
1963 for (int i = 0; i < node_size_original; i++) {
1964 if (IsNodeByLayoutOptimizer(graph_->node(i).name())) {
1965 return Status(error::INVALID_ARGUMENT,
1966 "The graph is already optimized by layout optimizer.");
1967 }
1968 if (ops_format_supported.find(graph_->node(i).op()) !=
1969 ops_format_supported.end()) {
1970 auto node = graph_->mutable_node(i);
1971 bool is_in_frame = !frames[node].empty();
1972 OptimizeContext opt_cxt(graph_, node, node_map_, graph_properties_,
1973 virtual_placer_, nodes_to_preserve_,
1974 is_in_frame);
1975 std::unique_ptr<NodeProcessor> node_processor;
1976 if (IsAvgPoolGrad(*node)) {
1977 node_processor.reset(new AvgPoolGradProcessor(opt_cxt));
1978 } else if (IsBiasAddGrad(*node)) {
1979 node_processor.reset(new BiasAddGradProcessor(opt_cxt));
1980 } else if (IsConv2D(*node)) {
1981 node_processor.reset(new Conv2DProcessor(opt_cxt, config_.no_gemm));
1982 } else if (IsConv2DBackpropFilter(*node)) {
1983 node_processor.reset(
1984 new Conv2DBackpropFilterProcessor(opt_cxt, config_.no_gemm));
1985 } else if (IsConv2DBackpropInput(*node)) {
1986 node_processor.reset(
1987 new Conv2DBackpropInputProcessor(opt_cxt, config_.no_gemm));
1988 } else if (IsDepthwiseConv2dNative(*node)) {
1989 node_processor.reset(new Conv2DProcessor(opt_cxt, true));
1990 } else if (IsDepthwiseConv2dNativeBackpropFilter(*node)) {
1991 node_processor.reset(
1992 new Conv2DBackpropFilterProcessor(opt_cxt, true));
1993 } else if (IsDepthwiseConv2dNativeBackpropInput(*node)) {
1994 node_processor.reset(new Conv2DBackpropInputProcessor(opt_cxt, true));
1995 } else if (IsFusedBatchNormGrad(*node)) {
1996 node_processor.reset(new FusedBatchNormGradProcessor(opt_cxt));
1997 } else if (IsMaxPoolV2(*node)) {
1998 node_processor.reset(new MaxPoolV2Processor(opt_cxt));
1999 } else if (IsMaxPoolGradV1(*node) || IsMaxPoolGradGradV1(*node)) {
2000 node_processor.reset(new MaxPoolGradProcessor(opt_cxt));
2001 } else if (IsMaxPoolGradV2(*node) || IsMaxPoolGradGradV2(*node)) {
2002 node_processor.reset(new MaxPoolGradV2Processor(opt_cxt));
2003 } else {
2004 node_processor.reset(new NodeProcessor(opt_cxt));
2005 }
2006 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(node_processor->ConvertNode());
2007 }
2008 }
2009
2010 // This is the second pass where we expand layout-agnostic nodes. This pass
2011 // only needs to be performed if at least one node in the previous pass is
2012 // expanded.
2013 if (graph_->node_size() > node_size_original) {
2014 NodeDef* n = AddNodePermNHWCToNCHW();
2015 n = AddNodePermNCHWToNHWC();
2016 std::set<string> ops_format_agnostic = GetOpsFormatAgnostic();
2017 for (int i = 0; i < graph_->node_size(); i++) {
2018 if (ops_format_agnostic.find(graph_->node(i).op()) !=
2019 ops_format_agnostic.end()) {
2020 auto node = graph_->mutable_node(i);
2021 bool is_in_frame = !frames[node].empty();
2022 OptimizeContext opt_cxt(graph_, node, node_map_, graph_properties_,
2023 virtual_placer_, nodes_to_preserve_,
2024 is_in_frame);
2025 std::unique_ptr<NodeProcessor> node_processor;
2026 if (IsAddN(*node)) {
2027 node_processor.reset(new AddNProcessor(opt_cxt));
2028 } else if (IsBetainc(*node)) {
2029 node_processor.reset(new TernaryOpProcessor(opt_cxt));
2030 } else if (IsBinaryOp(*node)) {
2031 node_processor.reset(new BinaryOpProcessor(opt_cxt));
2032 } else if (IsConcat(*node)) {
2033 node_processor.reset(new ConcatProcessor(opt_cxt));
2034 } else if (IsFill(*node)) {
2035 node_processor.reset(new FillProcessor(opt_cxt));
2036 } else if (IsHistogramSummary(*node)) {
2037 node_processor.reset(new HistogramSummaryProcessor(opt_cxt));
2038 } else if (IsIdentityN(*node)) {
2039 node_processor.reset(new IdentityNProcessor(opt_cxt));
2040 } else if (IsMerge(*node)) {
2041 node_processor.reset(new MergeProcessor(opt_cxt));
2042 } else if (IsPad(*node) || IsMirrorPad(*node) ||
2043 IsMirrorPadGrad(*node)) {
2044 node_processor.reset(new PadProcessor(opt_cxt));
2045 } else if (IsReduceOp(*node)) {
2046 node_processor.reset(new ReduceProcessor(opt_cxt));
2047 } else if (IsReverseV2(*node)) {
2048 node_processor.reset(new ReverseProcessor(opt_cxt));
2049 } else if (IsSelect(*node)) {
2050 node_processor.reset(new SelectProcessor(opt_cxt));
2051 } else if (IsSlice(*node)) {
2052 node_processor.reset(new SliceProcessor(opt_cxt));
2053 } else if (IsStridedSlice(*node)) {
2054 node_processor.reset(new StridedSliceProcessor(opt_cxt));
2055 } else if (IsShape(*node) || IsShapeN(*node)) {
2056 node_processor.reset(new ShapeProcessor(opt_cxt));
2057 } else if (IsSplit(*node)) {
2058 node_processor.reset(new SplitProcessor(opt_cxt));
2059 } else if (IsSplitV(*node)) {
2060 node_processor.reset(new SplitVProcessor(opt_cxt));
2061 } else if (IsSqueeze(*node)) {
2062 node_processor.reset(new SqueezeProcessor(opt_cxt));
2063 } else if (IsStridedSliceGrad(*node)) {
2064 node_processor.reset(new StridedSliceGradProcessor(opt_cxt));
2065 } else if (IsSwitch(*node)) {
2066 node_processor.reset(new SwitchProcessor(opt_cxt));
2067 } else if (IsTile(*node)) {
2068 node_processor.reset(new TileProcessor(opt_cxt));
2069 } else if (IsUnaryGrad(*node)) {
2070 node_processor.reset(new UnaryGradProcessor(opt_cxt));
2071 } else {
2072 node_processor.reset(new AgnosticNodeProcessor(opt_cxt));
2073 }
2074 TF_RETURN_IF_ERROR(node_processor->ConvertNode());
2075 }
2076 }
2077 }
2078 return Status::OK();
2079 }
2080
2081 // Remove all node pairs, where a NCHW-to-NHWC node is followed by
2082 // a NHWC-to-NCHW node.
2083 Status Collapse() {
2084 std::unordered_set<string> nodes_removable;
2085 for (int i = 0; i < graph_->node_size(); i++) {
2086 auto node = graph_->mutable_node(i);
2087 node->mutable_attr()->erase("_output_shapes");
2088 if (IsTransposeNHWCToNCHW(node->name()) ||
2089 IsDimMapNHWCToNCHW(node->name()) ||
2090 IsVecPermuteNHWCToNCHW(node->name())) {
2091 bool transpose_pair = IsTransposeNHWCToNCHW(node->name()) &&
2092 IsTransposeNCHWToNHWC(node->input(0));
2093 bool dim_map_pair = IsDimMapNHWCToNCHW(node->name()) &&
2094 IsDimMapNCHWToNHWC(node->input(0));
2095 bool vec_permute_pair = IsVecPermuteNHWCToNCHW(node->name()) &&
2096 IsVecPermuteNCHWToNHWC(node->input(0));
2097 if (transpose_pair || dim_map_pair || vec_permute_pair) {
2098 const string& trans_first = node->input(0);
2099 const string& trans_second = node->name();
2100 auto outputs = node_map_->GetOutputs(trans_second);
2101 CHECK(outputs.size() == 1)
2102 << "There is always only a single output for a Transpose node, "
2103 << "due to the way it is added by NodeProcessor.";
2104 NodeDef* output = *outputs.begin();
2105 string input = node_map_->GetNode(trans_first)->input(0);
2106 for (int i = 0; i < output->input_size(); i++) {
2107 if (output->input(i).compare(trans_second) == 0) {
2108 *output->mutable_input(i) = input;
2109 break;
2110 }
2111 }
2112 nodes_removable.insert(trans_first);
2113 nodes_removable.insert(trans_second);
2114 }
2115 }
2116 }
2117 graph_->mutable_node()->erase(
2118 std::remove_if(
2119 graph_->mutable_node()->begin(), graph_->mutable_node()->end(),
2120 [nodes_removable](const NodeDef& node) {
2121 return nodes_removable.find(node.name()) != nodes_removable.end();
2122 }),
2123 graph_->mutable_node()->end());
2124 return Status::OK();
2125 }
2126
2127 const LayoutOptimizer::TuningConfig& config_;
2128};

2130int GetNumGPUs(const Cluster& cluster) {
2131 auto devices = cluster.GetDevices();
2132 int num_gpus = 0;
2133 for (const auto& device : devices) {
2134 if (device.second.type() == "GPU") {
2135 if (device.second.environment().find("architecture") !=
2136 device.second.environment().end()) {
2137 const string arch = device.second.environment().at("architecture");
2138 // TODO(yaozhang): Enable for Volta GPUs (compute capability version 7).
2139 if (arch < "7") {
2140 num_gpus++;
2141 }
2142 }
2143 }
2144 }
2145 return num_gpus;
2146}

2149Status LayoutOptimizer::Tune(const GrapplerItem& item,
2150 const GraphProperties& graph_properties,
2151 const TuningConfig& config, GraphDef* output) {
2152 auto status = graph_properties.AnnotateOutputShapes(output);
2153 if (!status.ok()) {
2154 VLOG(1) << "Annotate shape return status: " << status.ToString();
2155 *output = item.graph;
2156 return status;
2157 }
2158 NodeMap node_map(output);
2159 DataLayoutOptimizer layout_optimizer(graph_properties, *virtual_placer_,
2160 config, nodes_to_preserve_, output,
2161 &node_map);
2162 status = layout_optimizer.Optimize();
2163 return status;
2164}
2165
2166Status LayoutOptimizer::Optimize(Cluster* cluster, const GrapplerItem& item,
2167 GraphDef* output) {
2168 if (cluster == nullptr) {
2169 return errors::InvalidArgument("cluster == nullptr");
2170 }
2171
2172 if (GetNumGPUs(*cluster) < 1) {
2173 // LayoutOptimizer is currently only tuned for GPU.
2174 *output = item.graph;
2175 return Status::OK();
2176 }
2177
2178 virtual_placer_.reset(new VirtualPlacer(cluster));
2179 nodes_to_preserve_ = item.NodesToPreserve();
2180 GraphProperties graph_properties(item);
2181 auto status = graph_properties.InferStatically(false);
2182 if (!status.ok()) {
2183 VLOG(1) << "Infer shape return status: " << status.ToString();
2184 *output = item.graph;
2185 return status;
2186 }
2187
2188 TuningConfig config;
2189 config.no_gemm = true;
2190 // TODO(yaozhang): Enable tuning with various TuningConfig choices wtih
2191 // the measurement-based estimator.
2192 status = Tune(item, graph_properties, config, output);
2193 if (!status.ok()) {
2194 *output = item.graph;
2195 }
2196 return status;
2197}
